            <div class="footer-section"><h3>‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶Ç‡¶ï</h3><a href="#" onclick="showPage('home')">‡¶π‡ßã‡¶Æ</a><a href="#" onclick="checkUser('write')">‡¶ó‡¶≤‡ßç‡¶™ ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ñ‡ßÅ‡¶®</a><a href="#" onclick="showPage('payment')">‡¶™‡ßá‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü</a></div>
